title: Journey - Novel Updates
tags: Male Protagonist   Management   Modern Day   Transmigration
author: Flying Pastoral Dog   飞翔的田园犬
description: Unproven young coach? But all of the coaches were once young! It's said that all of big names players have talents and so do coaches! Without hard work, even the best potential won't be reached! Traveling back in time and transmigrated into the body of an Englishman, Wen Sheng has only one goal in this life, it is to realize his dream of managing a football team, to fulfill his love and passion for football. He would experience joy and misery along his journey to the top.>
